## Session start checklist (for the AI assistant)

1. Read `docs/specs/spec.md` and `docs/specs/plan.md` if they exist.
2. Read `docs/standards/` in full.
3. Before implementing, confirm which BR-ID(s) this change serves. If none
   exists yet, propose one and update the spec first.
4. After implementing:
   - Confirm the corresponding Spock feature method
     `"BR-n: ..."` exists and passes (`./gradlew test`).
   - Run `./gradlew codenarcMain codenarcTest` — zero violations on changed
     files.
   - Confirm docs/README tables affected by this change are updated.
   - If GSP/JS was touched, confirm no raw/unencoded output was introduced
     and no inline `<script>` was added outside
     `grails-app/assets/javascripts/`.
